name: casablanca-info
description: Casablanca is a specialized npm package delivering curated static information about the captivating city of Casablanca. Developers can easily access a wealth of data, including details on landmarks, attractions, area, population, and more. With its user-friendly interface and meticulously organized content, Casablanca simplifies the integration of essential city insights into applications, providing users with valuable resources for exploring the vibrant cultural landscape of Casablanca.
author: yassine zemmouri <umpyassinez@gmail.com>
